<!-- dashboard.component.html -->
<app-header admNav1="Questions" admNav2="Highscore" admNav3="Category" [logOutBtn]="true" (admNav1Clicked)="activeComponent = 'question'" (admNav2Clicked)="activeComponent = 'highscore'" (admNav3Clicked)="activeComponent = 'category'"></app-header>

<app-category-highscore-page *ngIf="activeComponent === 'highscore'"></app-category-highscore-page>
<app-question-page *ngIf="activeComponent === 'question'"></app-question-page>
<app-category *ngIf="activeComponent === 'category'"></app-category>
import { Component } from '@angular/core';

@Component({
  selector: 'app-dashboard',
  templateUrl: './dashboard.component.html',
  styleUrls: ['./dashboard.component.css']
})
export class DashboardComponent {
  ngOnInit() {
    if(this.activeComponent === undefined){
      this.activeComponent == 'highscore';
      console.log("joel stinkt");
    } else{
      this.activeComponent == window.sessionStorage.getItem('activeComponent');
    }
  }
  activeComponent!: 'highscore' | 'question' | 'category';
}
